com.esri.mo2.file.shp
Interface MultiPartShape

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable
All Known Subinterfaces:
MultiPartShapeM, MultiPartShapeZ
All Known Implementing Classes:
MultiPatchShp, PolygonMShp, PolygonShp, PolygonZShp, PolylineMShp, PolylineShp, PolylineZShp
public interface MultiPartShape
extends Cloneable

This class declares the methods that are common to all multipart Shapes. When using these methods, the starting index for both point and part numbers is 0.
